    static let privacyPolicy:String = "Privacy Policy for the Gather Event App\n\nThe Gather Event app (the “App”) is committed to protecting the privacy of its users. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share personal information through the App. By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.\n\nInformation Collection\nWe collect personal information from users who create an account with the App. This information may include your name, email address, and other contact information. We may also collect information about your use of the App, such as the events you create or participate in and the content you upload or share through the App.\n\nInformation Use\nThe information we collect is used to provide and improve the services offered through the App. This includes allowing you to create and participate in events, as well as personalizing your experience with the App. We may also use your information to send you communications, such as emails and push notifications, regarding updates to the App or events you have created or joined.\n\nInformation Sharing\nWe will not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their marketing purposes without your consent. However, we may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in operating the App or providing services to you. These service providers are required to maintain the confidentiality of your information and use it only for the purposes for which it was disclosed.\n\nData Retention\nWe will retain your personal information for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide you with the services offered through the App. We will also retain your information as necessary to comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.\n\nData Security\nWe take the security of your personal information seriously and have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no data transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee the security of your information.\n\nUser Rights\nYou have the right to access, modify, or delete your personal information at any time. You may also request that we stop processing your information or that we provide it to you in a portable format. To exercise these rights, please contact us through the App.\n\nChanges to this Privacy Policy\nWe may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or to comply with legal requirements. Your continued use of the App after any changes have been made constitutes your acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.\n\nThis Privacy Policy was last updated on [Insert Date].\nIf you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us through the App."
    
    
